.TH "CSSVIEWTRANSITIONRULE.TYPES" "3JS" "December 9, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
CSSViewTransitionRule.types \- CSSViewTransitionRule: types property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]types\f[B]\f[R] read\-only property of the
\f[CR]CSSViewTransitionRule\f[R] interface returns an array containing
the associated \f[CR]\(atview\-transition\f[R] at\-rule\(cqs
\f[CR]types\f[R] descriptor values.
.SH VALUE
An array of strings.
.PP
If no \f[CR]types\f[R] descriptor is set on the
\f[CR]\(atview\-transition\f[R] at\-rule, the \f[CR]types\f[R] property
is equal to an empty array.
.SH EXAMPLES
See the main \f[CR]CSSViewTransitionRule\f[R] page for example usage.
.SH SEE ALSO
